FILENAME: gg_zaennon_tiny.bsp
FILESIZE: 1,96 MB
DATE RELEASED: 5 May 2009

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS: Place the gg_zaennon_tiny.bsp in "\Steam\steamapps\[username]\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps" folder, run the game and create server!

DESCRIPTION:
Fastpaced gungame map. Supports up to 36 players.
Enjoy!

BUGS: For the moment there are no known bugs, but if you notice anything please e-mail me so i can fix it.
